rows.label: bf05100150_0020
rows.name:
What's that?
Aren't they scared doing something like that?

rows.label: bf05100150_0030
rows.name:
It's a common game around here.
That's how they learn to swim in the Cloud Sea.

rows.label: bf05100150_0040
rows.name: Did you do it too, Rex?

rows.label: bf05100150_0060
rows.name:
When I became a salvager,
it was really useful.

rows.label: bf05100150_0070
rows.name:
I can't stand it down there. It's not like water,
feels like the clouds are wrapping around you.

rows.label: bf05100150_0080
rows.name: And you don't like heights, either.

rows.label: bf05100150_0090
rows.name:
If you practice diving, you'll get used to it quickly.
Want to try it here right now?

rows.label: bf05100150_0100
rows.name:
Hey, what are you doing?
Don't come near me, don't touch me!

rows.label: bf05100150_0110
rows.name: Stop that, Rex! Don't tease her.

rows.label: bf05100150_0130
rows.name: Geez, you're still such a child.
